data.description: Come check out this wonderful 2-story home located in the desirable Hollies at Westgate of Raeford! This home includes a formal dining room, a cozy living area with fireplace, and a galley kitchen with a separate eat-in nook! Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a huge bonus room! Both the roof and HVAC were recently replaced (2022), so you can be settled down here with sound peace of mind and just jump right into enjoying all of the amenities the Westgate community offers, such as the fitness center, outdoor pool, and playgrounds!  Don't miss out on this one!  Welcome home!
